children.subject: I have the same problem: telebears doesn't let me sign up for any 2nd session disc/lab so I can't get myself on the waitlist

history.content:
I'm not sure why there is an issue wait-listing the class; we have plenty of seats in all the discussion and lab sections, especially for EE 20 Section 2.  Please give it another try. 
If you run into the same issue, TeleBears has an option on the left hand sidebar where you can click "Waitlist Class" directly, and enter the CCN for the course.  If you have other issues, feel free to email me directly.

I was guaranteed a spot in EE 20 this fall semester. However, I am unable to add the second lecture (the class I wanted) to my waitlist for some reason. I had to add the first lecture instead since that was the only class I could waitlist. Is there anyone with this same problem? And what should I do about this? 

Thanks
